	tristate "use MAX17042 fuel gauge only as voltage tracking"
	default n
	depends on FUELGAUGE_MAX17042
	help
	 Say Y to use MAX17042 fuel gauge
	 only as voltage tracking.
	 This mode is for target that consumes low current
	 like smart-phone.

